<emphasis id="B970EAFEFFD3F63D8EFE35A1F7DCFE41" bold="true" box="[2016,2169,445,474]" pageId="23" pageNumber="81">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFD3F63D818C35A1F70DFD9A" authority="Hayman, 1947" authorityName="Hayman" authorityYear="1947" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Scotonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="81" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="zenkeri" subSpecies="occidentalis">Scotonycteris zenkeri occidentalis Hayman, 1947</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="3B6C3CB1FFD3F63D81A935F8F58AFD9A" box="[2231,2607,484,513]" pageId="23" pageNumber="81">
Oda, Oda Province, 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFD3F63D80D035F8F58EFD9A" box="[2510,2603,484,513]" name="Ghana" pageId="23" pageNumber="81">Ghana</collectingCountry>
.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFD3F63D8EFC361BF6DDFD5D" blockId="23.[2016,2611,445,868]" pageId="23" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFD3F63D8EFC361BF6AAFDB3" authorityName="Hayman" authorityYear="1947" box="[2018,2319,519,552]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Scotonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="81" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="occidentalis">Scotonycteris occidentalis</taxonomicName>
is very similar to and originally described as a subspecies of S. 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFD3F63D830B3633F785FDEC" authorityName="Matschie" authorityYear="1894" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Scotonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="81" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="zenkeri">zenkeri</taxonomicName>
but recently elevated to a distinct species based on analyses of cytochrome-b and nDNA sequences. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
